MERCURIES LIFE said unconsolidated sales
in December fell 7.11% to NT$11,128,662,000 from NT$11,980,327,000,
according to a statement filed to the  Taiwan Stock Exchange .  (Figures are in thousands of New Taiwan dollars)  =================================================================  12/2011          12/2010
Sales           11,128,662       11,980,327  
YOY%              -7.11%   -----------------Year-to-date-----------------
Sales          102,541,114      114,158,299  
YOY%             -10.18% 
=================================================================
 